'''''Lost in the Desert''''' ku '''''ikubitiro''''' yasohotse nka Dirkie, ni filime yo muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] y'Epfo yo mu 1969 yanditswe, yakozwe kandi iyobowe na Jamie Uys ku izina rya Jamie Hayes. Yafashwe amashusho muri Techniscope na Technicolor . Uys ubwe akina nka  Anton De Vries, umucuranzi wa piyano w'igitaramo cy'umuhungu we Dirkie wimyaka 8 . Dirkie akinishwa n'umuhungu wa Uys Wynand Uys, uzwi nka Dirkie Hayes.

Umugambi wahujwe nyuma yimyaka ibiri na "Walkabout" yatsinze cyane .

== Telugu remake ==
Isubiramo ryamamaye cyane ryakozwe mu rurimi rwa Telugu, ururimi rwo mu majyepfo [[Ubuhinde|y’Ubuhinde]], mu 1972, ku izina rya ''Papam Pasivadu''  hamwe n’impinduka nkeya zahinduwe mu nkuru kugira ngo zihuze n'abari aho.
